{"tid":2278041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"下周一開死因庭 恐真相未明","createTime":"2020-11-09T01:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T01:50:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"702aee6341f8b6fc8cacc0af769211dbfd34fd60","tid":2278041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T01:41:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201109/FNNHJC46DZC3JLC7H6YWA25LDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201109%2FFNNHJC46DZC3JLC7H6YWA25LDI%2F&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=54537841\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201109%2FFNNHJC46DZC3JLC7H6YWA25LDI%2F&h=dcdaf146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201109/FNNHJC46DZC3JLC7H6YWA25LDI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n下周一開死因庭 恐真相未明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7UVCmCR0kKFuWOgKn8E2DGC2Egc=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4DS2QKHL5BBW3LGHM6UYRGQFX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7UVCmCR0kKFuWOgKn8E2DGC2Egc%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4DS2QKHL5BBW3LGHM6UYRGQFX4.jpg&h=b7d3ced1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■周梓樂當日墮樓後，由救護員送院。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】死因庭下周一（16日）將就周梓樂死因展開研訊，屆時將傳召約60名證人，料審五周。案件或首次採用虛擬實境（VR）技術協助審案，省卻陪審團到現場考察，並能以第一身視角了解周梓樂墮樓原因。不過，昨日有悼念周梓樂的市民擔心，研訊未必可令真相大白，可能像浮屍大海的15歲少女陳彥霖被裁定死因存疑一樣，最終無法沉冤得雪。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：下周一開死因庭 恐真相未明<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將傳60證人<br />\n<br />\n據知，周梓樂的死因研訊將設五人陪審團，傳召約60名證人，包括現場救護員、義務急救員及警員，但醫管局、尚德邨一方或科大都不會加入聆訊成為與訟方；警方則獲准以有利害關係身份在正審列席。<br />\n<br />\n根據已公開資料，相信周梓樂是在尚德邨停車場三樓跌至二樓，。。。。。。。。。。，疑被延誤救治。警方就防暴警在墮樓發生前後何時進入停車場，說法亦曾前後不一。<br />\n<br />\n去年反修例運動中，撇除自殺抗議及。。。。。。。。。。訓局青年書院女生陳彥霖，死因庭早前裁定她「死因存疑」。"},{"pid":"9dc5e94ff4ae7d822a0170c79d86b247db046e89","tid":2278041,"uid":135488,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T01:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9p3cCXo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9p3cCXo.jpg&h=f5878abf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b41943a029bcdb8cef5d8996bd68141f64f9628","tid":2278041,"uid":234589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T01:50:49.000Z","msg":"黑狗阻礙救援已經係死罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}